{
  "stem": "21310.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I'm in-- in-- in a-- in a hurry to catch a train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I ran to the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so that was my, you know, my first experience and my first experience with real, you know, chutzpah, that really saved me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I had several other experiences.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At one point, my-- I was taking a train-- oh.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, I should go back to my work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I worked at the railroad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was translating different directives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I was-- this stationmaster liked me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I gained his confidence.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he put me in charge of-- of food stamps because the-- the railroad people were getting supplementary food stamps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so he put me in charge of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this station was in charge of some other substations, some smaller-- so that we had quite a number of employees.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I immediately started to steal some of these additional food stamps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I made, like, two lists of employees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they didn't check.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I would just request it, you know, from the main-- main station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know where it-- don't remember where it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I need so many, for so many employees, and [LAUGHS] they would just send it to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had these additional food stamps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I also was able to steal a railroad ID card.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These people who-- railroad people worked-- were getting special identity cards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- I knew where they were kept.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were actually kept under lock and key.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would steal-- like, every couple of days, I would steal one or two.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I would give them to the-- to the underground.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the person who gave me the-- the first false ID.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would-- he worked for the underground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] What else?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
